Info }: { captureInfo: CaptureInfo }) {\\n  const camera = useRef(null);\\n \\n  return (\\n    \\n  );\\n}\\nProps:\\n\\ncaptureInfo (required) - From initCapture()\\nposition - Camera to use: &quot;front&quot; or &quot;back&quot; (default: &quot;back&quot;)\\nisActive - Whether camera is running (default: true)\\nstyle - Style for the camera view\\n\\n\",\"title\":\"ZCamera\",\"titles\":[\"Capture SDK\",\"API Reference\"]},{\"href\":\"/sdk/capture#zcameratakephoto\",\"html\":\"\\n<p>Captures a photo and returns a signed <code>ZPhoto</code>.</p>\\n<pre class=\\\"shiki shiki-themes github-light github-dark-dimmed\\\" style=\\\"background-color:#fff;--shiki-dark-bg:#22272e;color:#24292e;--shiki-dark:#adbac7\\\" tabindex=\\\"0\\\"><code><span class=\\\"line\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#D73A49;--shiki-dark:#F47067\\\">const</span><span style=\\\"color:#005CC5;--shiki-dark:#6CB6FF\\\"> photo</span><span style=\\\"color:#D73A49;--shiki-dark:#F47067\\\"> =</span><span style=\\\"color:#D73A49;--shiki-dark:#F47067\\\"> await</span><span style=\\\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#ADBAC7\\\"> camera.current?.</span><span style=\\\"color:#6F42C1;--shiki-dark:#DCBDFB\\\">takePhoto</span><span style=\\\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#ADBAC7\\\">();</span></span>\\n<span class=\\\"line\\\" data-empty-line=\\\"true\\\"> </span>\\n<span class=\\\"line\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#ADBAC7\\\">console.</span><span style=\\\"color:#6F42C1;--shiki-dark:#DCBDFB\\\">log</span><span style=\\\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#ADBAC7\\\">(photo.originalPath); </span><span style=\\\"color:#6A737D;--shiki-dark:#768390\\\">// Raw capture path</span></span>\\n<span class=\\\"line\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#ADBAC7\\\">console.</span><span style=\\\"color:#6F42C1;--shiki-dark:#DCBDFB\\\">log</span><span style=\\\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#ADBAC7\\\">(photo.path);         </span><span style=\\\"color:#6A737D;--shiki-dark:#768390\\\">// C2PA-signed photo path</span></span></code></pre>\\n<p><strong>Returns:</strong> <code>ZPhoto</code> with:</p>\\n<ul>\\n<li><code>originalPath</code> - Path to the raw captured image</li>\\n<li><code>path</code> - Path to the C2PA-signed image with <code>succinct.bindings</code></li>\\n</ul>\\n\",\"id\":\"docs/pages/sdk/capture.mdx#zcameratakephoto\",\"isPage\":false,\"text\":\"\\nCaptures a photo and returns a signed ZPhoto.\\nconst photo = await camera.current?.takePhoto();\\n \\nconsole.log(photo.originalPath); // Raw capture path\\nconsole.log(photo.path);         // C2PA-signed photo path\\nReturns: ZPhoto with:\\n\\noriginalPath - Path to the raw captured image\\npath - Path to the C2PA-signed image with succinct.bindings\\n\\n\",\"title\":\"ZCamera.takePhoto()\",\"titles\":[\"Capture SDK\",\"API Reference\"]},{\"href\":\"/sdk/capture#complete-example\",\"html\":\"\\n<pre class=\\\"shiki shiki-themes github-light github-dark-dimmed\\\" style=\\\"background-color:#fff;--shiki-dark-bg:#22272e;color:#24292e;--shiki-dark:#adbac7\\\" tabindex=\\\"0\\\"><code><span class=\\\"line\\\" data-empty-line=\\\"true\\\"> </span>\\n<span class=\\\"line\\\" data-empty-line=\\\"true\\\"> </span>\\n<span class=\\\"line\\\" data-empty-line=\\\"true\\\"> </span>\\n<span class=\\\"line\\\" data-empty-line=\\\"true\\\"> </span>\\n<span class=\\\"line\\\" data-empty-line=\\\"true\\\"> </span>\\n<span class=\\\"line\\\" data-empty-line=\\\"true\\\"> </span>\\n<span class=\\\"line\\\" data-empty-line=\\\"true\\\"> </span>\\n<span class=\\\"line\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#D73A49;--shiki-dark:#F47067\\\">  const</span><span style=\\\"color:#005CC5;--shiki-dark:#6CB6FF\\\"> camera</span><span style=\\\"color:#D73A49;--shiki-dark:#F47067\\\"> =</span><span style=\\\"color:#6F42C1;--shiki-dark:#DCBDFB\\\"> useRef</span><span style=\\\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#ADBAC7\\\">(</span><span style=\\\"color:#005CC5;--shiki-dark:#6CB6FF\\\">null</span><span style=\\\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#ADBAC7\\\">);</span></span>\\n<span 